) 26. Rxd1 Rxd1 27. Qxd1 Qd6 $1 {The exchange of the queens is practically
forced since the black queen is ready to invade White's camp.} 28. Qxd6 Bxd6
$17 {[%csl Ra5][%cal Yd6c7] and Black wins a pawn.} *

