some problems after} 18. Bh6 {[%csl Ge6] Calculate what the best move for
Black is and what is the evaluation of the position?} Bf6 $1 {The strongest
idea for Black involves an exchange sacrifice.} (18... Nc5 $2 {on other hand,
is just bad:} 19. Bxg7 Kxg7 20. b4 $1 {and Black loses material} Bf6 21. Qe3
