[%cal Ge8d8]}) (13. Rfc1 d5 $1 {equalized immediately in Anand,V (2762)
-Gelfand,B (2681) FIDE World Cup KO 2000 (2.1) 1/2-1/2} 14. e5 Ne4 $1 $132)
13... Qc7 14. h3 {Usually, such positions are preferred by technical players,
who like to play slowly and to improve their positions by seizing small
