exd5 (12. Qxd5 Qc7 $1 {[%csl Gc2][%cal Yd7b6,Gc8b7] the rook is taboo}) 12...
a5 $1 {[%cal Gc8a6] this was the reason for Black to keep the bishop on c8 as
it is possible to develop it on the more useful diagonal a6-f1.} 13. O-O {
and now} h5 $1 {gives the initiative to Black on the kingside.} 14. gxh5 (14. Ng3
