10... Bb7 11. g4 Nc5 12. Ng3 O-O 13. Nf5 $5 {If White wants to play this move,
he must rush.} (13. Re1 g6 $1 14. Bh6 Re8 15. Qd2 Ne6 $132 {[%csl Gd4,Gf4]}) {
Black is the one who must be careful now and play} 13... Rb8 $1 $146 {and
