c3 Qc7 {[%csl Yc3]} 24. Ba6 bxc3 $1 25. bxc3 (25. Bxc8 $2 cxb2 $19) 25... Ra8
26. Bb5 Rc8 27. Ra3 Bc4 $1 28. Bxc4 Rxc4 {and White still cannot make any
progress.}) 23... R8c6 {c7 should be available to the queen.} 24. Bb5 Rc8 {
In fact, Black's pressure on the c-file is enough to keep White passive, or he
simply regains the pawn. White did not find anything better than repeating
moves with} 25. Ba6 $11 {Navara,D (2745) -Wojtaszek,R (2744) Vugar Gashimov
Mem 2018 2018 (3.1) 1/2-1/2} *

