go for this move and after} 14. Bg5 Nh5 $5 {embark in the forced line} 15. Nxe5
$1 (15. Bxe7 Qxe7 16. Nxe5 $2 Nf4 $19) 15... Bxg5 16. Qxh5 Bf6 17. Nf3 Bxc3 18.
bxc3 Qxc3 19. Nd4 $14 {in which Black may achieve the draw due to the
simplifications, but in practice, White retains a small advantage due to the
