$1 {this improvement of the queen is another point of Qe8} 16. Qd3 (16. f3 $142
) 16... Bxc4 17. Qxc4 Qxc4 18. bxc4 Rfc8 19. Ra4 b5 $1 {a well-timed move.} 20.
cxb5 axb5 21. Rxa8 Rxa8 $132 {Bittencourt,J (2448)-Di Berardino,D (2430)
