is enough to equalize.} 16. Bb6 (16. exd5 Bb4 $1 {at least regains the pawn}
17. Bb6 Qd7 18. Nd3 Bxc3 19. Qxc3 Nxd5 20. Nxe5 Qf5 $1 21. Qd4 Nf4 $36) 16...
