16... Qd7 $2 17. b3 $16) 17. Nxd5 (17. exd5 Bb4 18. d6 Qd7 {Black is a tempo
down now, but it is still enough to equalize} 19. Nd3 Bxd6 20. Nxe5 Bxe5 21.
Qxd7 Nxd7 22. Rxd7 Bxc3 23. bxc3 Bb5 $1 24. Rxb7 Rxc3 $11) 17... Nxe4 18. Qe1
f5 19. Nxe7+ Qxe7 $11 {Smeets,J (2669) -Giri,A (2677) Bundesliga 1011 2010 (5.
1) 0-1} *

