Bxe4+ 19. Qxe4 Bxg5 $19) 16... e4 $1 {[%cal Gb7h1,Ye8e1] Black uses the open
lines to the maximum.} 17. Bg2 (17. Nxe4 Nxe4 18. Bxe4 Bd6 {[%cal Rd8h4,Gd7f6]
and White is lost} 19. Qg2 Rxe4 $1 20. Qxe4 Nf6 $19 {[%csl Rh1][%cal Rb7d5]
this is why usually g4 is not good if d5 works because Black will get a
powerful attack.}) 17... Nxd5 18. Nxe4 N7f6 $36 {Hjartarson,J (2536)-Vidit,S 
(2670) Reykjavik op 2017 (4) 0-1 And Black had a strong initiative in} *

